      public TwoStageResult(double totalFlow, String flowUnit, Map<String,Double> trainSplits, Map<String,Double> trainFlows, Map<String,Double> trainUtilizations, Map<String,Double> trainPowers, Map<String,Double> trainSurgeMargins, ProductionOptimizer.OptimizationResult stage1Result, ProductionOptimizer.OptimizationResult stage2Result)
      Constructs a two-stage result.
      Parameters:
      totalFlow - optimal total flow rate
      flowUnit - flow rate unit
      trainSplits - split fractions per train
      trainFlows - flow rates per train
      trainUtilizations - utilization per train
      trainPowers - power consumption per train (kW)
      trainSurgeMargins - surge margin per train
      stage1Result - result from load balancing stage
      stage2Result - result from throughput maximization stage
